Oh, I think all of us would say, I want God's favor and I want God's blessing.

714
00:43:46,340 --> 00:43:49,540
But the pathway to blessing is obedience.

715
00:43:49,540 --> 00:43:53,220
The pathway to blessing is obedience.

716
00:43:53,220 --> 00:43:54,220
Let us pray.

717
00:43:54,220 --> 00:43:55,340
Father, we love You.

718
00:43:55,340 --> 00:43:56,540
We thank You for loving us.

719
00:43:56,540 --> 00:44:01,460
We thank You this morning for Your Word and for the truth of Your Word.

720
00:44:02,020 --> 00:44:11,220
We thank You that You have recorded this passage of this moment between father and son, David

721
00:44:11,220 --> 00:44:12,220
and Solomon.

722
00:44:12,220 --> 00:44:17,980
God, I pray that as we take time this morning to analyze it, that we would be careful to

723
00:44:17,980 --> 00:44:25,660
apply truth in our lives, that we would evaluate our own lives to see how we're doing in our

724
00:44:25,660 --> 00:44:29,660
