725
00:44:29,660 --> 00:44:33,020
Lord, help us to live lives that are obedient.

726
00:44:33,020 --> 00:44:40,780
Lord, help us to have a desire to influence and impact a future generation, that they

727
00:44:40,780 --> 00:44:45,340
would not only hear our words as we see in the life of Paul, that they would hear, but

728
00:44:45,340 --> 00:44:50,100
also that they would see in us a life of obedience.

729
00:44:50,100 --> 00:44:52,180
Lord, we want Your favor.

730
00:44:52,180 --> 00:44:54,340
We want Your blessing.

731
00:44:54,660 --> 00:45:00,140
Lord, we know that that pathway to blessing is marked by obedience.

732
00:45:00,140 --> 00:45:03,060
I pray that You would work in hearts and lives this morning.

733
00:45:03,060 --> 00:45:09,020
We started out by talking about the fact that David was going to die.

734
00:45:09,020 --> 00:45:13,260
Maybe this morning, you're here and you do not know that heaven is your home.

735
00:45:13,260 --> 00:45:18,340
In fact, you might say that I hope that when I die, I'd go to heaven.

736
00:45:18,340 --> 00:45:19,340
I think so.

737
00:45:19,340 --> 00:45:21,140
I hope so.

738
00:45:21,140 --> 00:45:25,580
But the reality this morning is that you just do not know with certainty that heaven is

739
00:45:25,580 --> 00:45:26,580
your home.

740
00:45:26,580 --> 00:45:30,060
There's never been a time in your life that you were born again, that you were saved by

741
00:45:30,060 --> 00:45:31,060
the grace of God.

742
00:45:31,060 --> 00:45:34,940
Can I tell you this morning that we'd love to take a Bible and show you how you can know

743
00:45:34,940 --> 00:45:38,740
for sure that heaven is your home.

744
00:45:38,740 --> 00:45:39,740
I would not embarrass you.

745
00:45:39,740 --> 00:45:42,220
I'm not going to ask you to raise your hand or any of that sort of thing, but we would

746
00:45:42,220 --> 00:45:47,180
invite you to come in our invitation time so that we might take a Bible and show you

747
00:45:47,180 --> 00:45:50,540
so you could leave here knowing with certainty that heaven is your home.

748
00:45:50,540 --> 00:45:53,260
How about you, child of God?

749
00:45:53,260 --> 00:46:02,140
Is your life marked by obedience, keeping the statutes, commandments, judgments, testimonies

750
00:46:02,140 --> 00:46:07,940
of the Lord, doing, walking in the ways of the Lord, seeking to please, honor, and glorify

751
00:46:07,940 --> 00:46:08,940
Him?

752
00:46:08,940 --> 00:46:14,980
Lord, I pray that You would work in the moments that follow, that You'd have Your will in

