00:46:14,980 --> 00:46:18,620
one way, that You'd be honored and glorified through every decision, and we'll thank You

754
00:46:18,620 --> 00:46:19,620
for it.

755
00:46:19,620 --> 00:46:20,620
In Christ's name we pray.

756
00:46:20,620 --> 00:46:21,620
Would you stand with me?

757
00:46:21,620 --> 00:46:22,620
Heads are bowed.

758
00:46:22,620 --> 00:46:24,100
Eyes are closed.

759
00:46:24,100 --> 00:46:25,660
Kimberly's going to play quietly on the piano.

760
00:46:25,660 --> 00:46:27,060
As she does, the altar is open.

761
00:46:27,060 --> 00:46:29,300
If you're not sure of heaven, please come.

762
00:46:29,300 --> 00:46:32,380
We take a Bible and show you how you can know for sure that heaven is your home.

763
00:46:32,380 --> 00:46:35,660
If you're saved this morning, say, I want God's favor in my life.

764
00:46:35,660 --> 00:46:40,540
